VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT source_address_prefix\s*=\s*"\*"[^}]*direction\s*=\s*"Inbound"|direction\s*=\s*"Inbound"[^}]*source_address_prefix\s*=\s*"\*"
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:source_address_prefix\s*=\s*"\*"|source_address_prefix\s*=\s*"Internet" && PRESENT:access\s*=\s*"Allow" && MISSING:# intentional|# required|egress
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects Azure NSG rules that allow all inbound traffic from any source.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Azure NSG Rule Allows All Inbound Traffic.
